################################################################################
# t/partition_value_ndb.test                                                   #
#                                                                              #
# Purpose:                                                                     #
#  Tests around "exotic" values calculated by the partitioning function        #
#        NDB branch                                                            #
#                                                                              #
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
# Original Author: mleich                                                      #
# Original Date: 2006-04-11                                                    #
# Change Author: mleich                                                        #
# Change Date: 2008-12-08                                                      #
